ss="zm-noti7-content-body"><div class="zm-noti7-popup-loading"><span class="noti-spinner-loading"></span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="zm-noti7-frame-border bottom"></div><div class="zm-noti7-popup-footer"><a href="/notifications" class="zm-noti7-popup-footer-all zg-right">查看全部 &raquo;</a><a href="/settings/notification" class="zm-noti7-popup-footer-set" title="通知设置" ><i class="zg-icon zg-icon-settings"></i></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="zu-global-notify" id="zh-global-message" style="display:none"><div class="zg-wrap"><div class="zu-global-nitify-inner"><a class="zu-global-notify-close" href="javascript:;" title="关闭" name="close">x</a><span class="zu-global-notify-icon"></span><span class="zu-global-notify-msg"></span></div></div></div><main class="pure-g receptacle"><section class="page-content-main pure-u-1 pure-u-md-17-24"><div class="unit-inner"><div class="module roundtable-profile clearfix"><a href="/roundtable/haojiaju" class="photo visible-desktop"><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-118d00f56500000048afe6b519048180_xl.jpg" srcset="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-118d00f56500000048afe6b519048180_b.jpg 2x" alt="买一件好家具" class="avatar"></a><div class="content"><div class="title"><h1><a href="/roundtable/haojiaju">买一件好家具</a></h1><span class="status">已结束</span></div><div class="description">想实用有颜，质量好价格优，还得环保不被坑。如何才能买到一件称心好家具，是我们每个人居家生活中所要面对的一个重要议题。本次圆桌将携手业内专业人士，就大家所关心的重点话题分享经验，一起聊聊买家具的那些事儿。</div><div class="actions"><button class="button-link share pull-left" data-id="286" data-token="haojiaju"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button><span class="visits text-muted">28437248 次浏览 </span><span class="bull">&bull;</span><a href="/roundtable/haojiaju/followers" class="followers text-muted"><span class="count" data-count="5789"> 5789</span> 人关注</a></div></div></div><div class="module"><ul class="menu-nav horizontal"><li ><a href="/roundtable/haojiaju">67 <span class="nowrap">条动态</span></a></li><li ><a href="/roundtable/haojiaju/questions">34 <span class="nowrap">个问题</span></a></li><li ><a href="/roundtable/haojiaju/comments">13 <span class="nowrap">条讨论</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="feeds loose user-answers"><ul class="items" data-paging><li class="item" data-type="Answer"><a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-115860060"></a><link itemprop="url" href="/question/30091807/answer/471847268"><meta itemprop="question-id" content="4219182"><meta itemprop="question-url-token" content="30091807"><meta itemprop="answer-id" content="115860060"><meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="471847268"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="js-title-link" target="_blank" href="/question/30091807/answer/471847268">二手家具有哪些回收再利用的好方法？</a></h2></div><article class="entry answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>6</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">6</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/yang-sha-sha-68-47" data-hovercard='p$t$yang-sha-sha-68-47'>sasha</a>，<span title="家具设计师~ 原创家具品牌着调zhaodiao主理人" class="bio">家具设计师~ 原创家具品牌着调zhaodiao主理人</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="sasha" data-entry-url="/question/30091807/answer/471847268"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand">二手家具很多使用功能上好，可能是局部损坏，或者表面陈旧，或者年代久远，风格不再流行，与新环境不搭，但是进行一些改造后，还是可以很好的重新使用 1、很多实木类，表面陈旧，最简单的，可以重新打磨，刷漆。一般来说，黑色或者白色都是比较保险的颜色，…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/30091807/answer/471847268">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="6"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/yang-wu-80-87" data-hovercard='p$t$yang-wu-80-87'>yang wu</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/ban-ye-hong" data-hovercard='p$t$ban-ye-hong'>我的小龙虾</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/yoyo-cheung-95" data-hovercard='p$t$yoyo-cheung-95'>不穿鞋子的猫</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content"><p>二手家具很多使用功能上好，可能是局部损坏，或者表面陈旧，或者年代久远，风格不再流行，与新环境不搭，但是进行一些改造后，还是可以很好的重新使用</p><p><br></p><p>1、很多实木类，表面陈旧，最简单的，可以重新打磨，刷漆。</p><p>一般来说，黑色或者白色都是比较保险的颜色，容易出效果。</p><p>柜子类，也可以换一些小的配件，如拉手，简单黄铜拉手或者皮质拉手等，也可以改变下整个柜子的气质。</p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a8f80f87642fc9197da5d5a76ce2400f_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="453" data-rawheight="720" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-beef577622f95dbb3d0b75ba49d34462_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="453" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a8f80f87642fc9197da5d5a76ce2400f_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-584f659931d558252655de048dbdc30c_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="426" data-rawheight="918" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-31358baf2c5b25ee7a4cc55b7f24a5dc_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="426" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-584f659931d558252655de048dbdc30c_r.jpg"></figure><p>有能力手绘的还可以做一些图案创作，但是这种要看家里风格，大概一两个有个点缀即可，不适合大面积使用。</p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2477661995342684a302355cd121a08a_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="291" data-rawheight="516" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-c316b41493726b30a8f5639411c1e8f2_b.jpg" class="content_image" width="291"></figure><p>或者是用一些装饰贴纸胶带，下图是我读书时候用胶带贴的一个坏了的铁锅，可以做桌上收纳～</p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-4213a0c013d453181c4c43931fd96870_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="670" data-rawheight="502" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-45d8c1e3673d273e9c1e2687f063973b_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="670" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-4213a0c013d453181c4c43931fd96870_r.jpg"></figure><p>2、形式老旧或者局部损毁，除去表面上漆外，还可以进行结构上的拆解和组合。</p><p>特别是带抽屉部件，本身就可以拿出来做单独的收纳盒。可以上墙，也可以加腿，变站立的边柜等等。</p><p>除此之外，带横杆的家具部件多可以改变用来做挂物品的墙挂。</p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a9437c33b296a6f3cf364db9e0ac0c6a_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="564" data-rawheight="1167" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-3bf803c34388440a9d5a14825d8a9974_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="564" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a9437c33b296a6f3cf364db9e0ac0c6a_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-d8f0da25dae8b486ca3f4a914789c0de_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="564" data-rawheight="862" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-74253591fc9364a71e1b557bcdbed911_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="564" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-d8f0da25dae8b486ca3f4a914789c0de_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9b4e51b2a8d3cf3892457d750e56877f_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="236" data-rawheight="577" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-c899fdf318974e83549d2d486cb01850_b.jpg" class="content_image" width="236"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-69ac003db802c81ef4ce99c818933a13_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="298" data-rawheight="642" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-26203fcb0a909a8fb61e4d2bb938f416_b.jpg" class="content_image" width="298"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5a06be8c7d41f8892c62a97415b9020d_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="973" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-61cf00a5f2ab160ade9c6307a73ed6e8_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="550" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5a06be8c7d41f8892c62a97415b9020d_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-7b912772ad3558bf537062ec5bc958a4_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="564" data-rawheight="1057" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a9e5864e040a75062340cda3ff1a1f97_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="564" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-7b912772ad3558bf537062ec5bc958a4_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-219af1ad9e67c80eb0524886629f99ee_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="564" data-rawheight="1108" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-6dc84d5bc9e5f9cf0cf72871ef11f3a5_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="564" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-219af1ad9e67c80eb0524886629f99ee_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a0df01c6c5ab5720153e0ce43a30da86_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="889" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-baf7cbd11e9c9673b10fd5a6c4a96cdb_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a0df01c6c5ab5720153e0ce43a30da86_r.jpg"></figure><p>3.软包家具。最简单的是买一块纹理图案比较有设计感的布盖住，试用于沙发，餐桌等，或者找人做个布套，如果动手能力强了，还可以替换掉海绵，重新软包。</p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b9529fff3d10ee0c6076c60cec7aad16_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="548" data-rawheight="700" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-13ed03c47385d8e0b6a76101a6591e3d_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="548" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b9529fff3d10ee0c6076c60cec7aad16_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-227c37267df44dbd23c16cdf82c3275d_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="611" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-413c3043be63d41c704d3be2de2ae36c_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="550" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-227c37267df44dbd23c16cdf82c3275d_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-f67b56a17538f9972ad34ad7b674ef66_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="236" data-rawheight="314" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b5c07d982e878a176345a7fa23be5d54_b.jpg" class="content_image" width="236"></figure></script><a class="time" href="/question/30091807/answer/471847268">2018-08-18</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>6</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="4219182"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">添加评论</span></button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-thank "><i class="fi fi-thank"></i>感谢</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-share"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-collect"><i class="fi fi-fav"></i>收藏</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-report"><i class="fi fi-report"></i>举报</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="1"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6c5bdf2b4fd218f329688af117bdf571_m.jpg"><meta name="own" content="true"><a href="/terms#sec-licence-1" target="_blank" class="action-item js-copyright">作者保留权利</a></li><li class="hidden-phone item-collapse js-collapse"><button cl